This paper discusses the management and analysis of data in IoT environments, which involves information retrieval (IR) and database (DB) techniques. It also covers the quality of data, which is a concern in cybersecurity (CYBER) and distributed computing (DC). Additionally, the paper touches on social implications (SI) of IoT, such as how data is used in society.
